<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>物流枢纽能力峰值预警看板</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/echarts@5.4.3/dist/echarts.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/echarts@5.4.3/dist/echarts.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background: #0a1628;
            color: #e0e6ed;
            height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .app-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            height: 100vh;
            padding: 10px;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        /* 顶部导航 */
        .top-nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 8px 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a2744 0%, #0d1a30 100%);
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #2a3f5f;
            min-height: 50px;
        }

        .nav-left {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .system-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #4fc3f7, #81c784);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .tab-group {
            display: flex;
            gap: 5px;
        }

        .tab-btn {
            padding: 6px 18px;
            border: 1px solid #3a5a7a;
            background: transparent;
            color: #8899aa;
            border-radius: 6px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 13px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .tab-btn.active {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2979ff, #1565c0);
            color: #fff;
            border-color: #2979ff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(41, 121, 255, 0.3);
        }

        .tab-btn:hover:not(.active) {
            background: rgba(41, 121, 255, 0.1);
            color: #4fc3f7;
        }

        .nav-right {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .time-display {
            color: #4fc3f7;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .status-dot {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #4caf50;
            animation: pulse-dot 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse-dot {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0.4; }
        }

        /* 主要内容区域 - 网格 */
        .main-content {
            flex: 1;
            display: grid;
            gap: 10px;
            min-height: 0;
        }

        /* 实时驾驶舱布局 */
        .layout-realtime {
            grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr;
            grid-template-rows: auto 1fr auto;
        }

        .layout-realtime > .top-summary {
            grid-column: 1 / -1;
        }

        .layout-realtime > .alert-panel {
            grid-row: 2 / 4;
        }

        /* 班次看板布局 */
        .layout-shift {
            grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
            grid-template-rows: auto 1fr;
        }

        .layout-shift > .shift-summary {
            grid-column: 1 / -1;
        }

        /* 日级分析/精益布局 */
        .layout-daily {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
            grid-template-rows: auto 1fr auto;
        }

        .layout-daily > .daily-summary {
            grid-column: 1 / -1;
        }

        .layout-daily > .bottleneck-chart {
            grid-column: 1 / 3;
        }

        .layout-daily > .optimization-panel {
            grid-column: 1 / -1;
        }

        /* 通用卡片样式 */
        .card {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #0f1f3d, #162a4a);
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #2a3f5f;
            padding: 14px;
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .card-title {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #8899bb;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .card-title .badge {
            font-size: 11px;
            padding: 2px 8px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background: #1a2f4a;
            color: #4fc3f7;
        }

        /* 预警灯 */
        .alert-gauge {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .gauge-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            padding: 6px 10px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
            border-radius: 6px;
            border-left: 3px solid #4caf50;
        }

        .gauge-item.red { border-left-color: #f44336; }
        .gauge-item.orange { border-left-color: #ff9800; }
        .gauge-item.yellow { border-left-color: #ffeb3b; }
        .gauge-item.green { border-left-color: #4caf50; }

        .gauge-label {
            flex: 1;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .gauge-value {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .gauge-value.red { color: #f44336; }
        .gauge-value.orange { color: #ff9800; }
        .gauge-value.yellow { color: #ffeb3b; }
        .gauge-value.green { color: #4caf50; }

        /* 进度条 */
        .progress-bar {
            width: 80px;
            height: 6px;
            background: #1a2f4a;
            border-radius: 3px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .progress-fill {
            height: 100%;
            border-radius: 3px;
            transition: width 0.5s;
        }

        /* 建议面板 */
        .suggestion-list {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        .suggestion-item {
            padding: 6px 10px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 13px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .suggestion-item .icon {
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .suggestion-item .priority-high {
            color: #f44336;
        }

        .suggestion-item .priority-medium {
            color: #ff9800;
        }

        .suggestion-item .priority-low {
            color: #4caf50;
        }

        /* 图表容器 */
        .chart-container {
            flex: 1;
            min-height: 0;
        }

        /* 预测面板 */
        .forecast-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .forecast-item {
            padding: 8px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .forecast-time {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #8899bb;
        }

        .forecast-value {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 4px 0;
        }

        /* 响应式 */
        @media (max-width: 1400px) {
            .layout-realtime {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            }
            .layout-daily {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 1000px) {
            .top-nav {
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                gap: 8px;
            }
            .layout-realtime, .layout-shift, .layout-daily {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                grid-template-rows: auto;
            }
            .forecast-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            }
        }

        /* 隐藏切换 */
        .view-hidden {
            display: none !important;
        }

        /* 时间线 */
        .timeline-container {
            display: flex;
            gap: 6px;
            align-items: flex-end;
            height: 100%;
            min-height: 60px;
        }

        .timeline-bar {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 4px;
        }

        .timeline-bar .bar {
            width: 100%;
            min-height: 8px;
            border-radius: 3px 3px 0 0;
            transition: height 0.5s;
        }

        .timeline-bar .time-label {
            font-size: 10px;
            color: #667799;
        }

        /* 按钮动画 */
        .pulse-btn {
            animation: pulse-border 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse-border {
            0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(41, 121, 255, 0.4); }
            50% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(41, 121, 255, 0); }
        }

        /* 滚动条 */
        .scrollable {
            overflow-y: auto;
            flex: 1;
        }

        .scrollable::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 4px;
        }

        .scrollable::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: #0a1628;
        }

        .scrollable::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: #2a3f5f;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        /* 配置面板（浮层） */
        .config-panel {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
            z-index: 100;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .config-panel.open {
            display: flex;
        }

        .config-content {
            background: #0f1f3d;
            border: 1px solid #2a3f5f;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 24px;
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 800px;
            max-height: 80vh;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }

        .config-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .config-table th, .config-table td {
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #1a2f4a;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .config-table th {
            color: #4fc3f7;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .config-table input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 4px 8px;
            background: #0a1628;
            border: 1px solid #2a3f5f;
            border-radius: 4px;
            color: #e0e6ed;
        }

        .config-close {
            float: right;
            background: none;
            border: none;
            color: #8899aa;
            font-size: 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="app-container">
        <!-- 顶部导航 -->
        <nav class="top-nav">
            <div class="nav-left">
                <span class="system-title">🚚 物流枢纽能力峰值预警</span>
                <div class="tab-group">
                    <button class="tab-btn active" data-view="realtime">🚀 实时驾驶舱</button>
                    <button class="tab-btn" data-view="shift">📊 班次看板</button>
                    <button class="tab-btn" data-view="daily">📈 精益管理</button>
                    <button class="tab-btn pulse-btn" onclick="openConfig()">⚙️ 配置</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="nav-right">
                <span class="status-dot"></span>
                <span>系统运行正常</span>
                <span>|</span>
                <span class="time-display" id="currentTime">--:--:--</span>
            </div>
        </nav>

        <!-- 实时驾驶舱视图 -->
        <div id="view-realtime" class="main-content layout-realtime">
            <!-- 顶部摘要 -->
            <div class="card top-summary">
                <div class="card-title">
                    <span>📊 实时概览 <span class="badge">最后更新：15秒前</span></span>
                    <span style="font-size:13px;color:#4fc3f7;">预测未来2小时峰值：<strong style="color:#ff9800;">120%</strong></span>
                </div>
                <div class="forecast-grid">
                    <div class="forecast-item">
                        <div class="forecast-time">当前利用率</div>
                        <div class="forecast-value" style="color:#ff9800;">95%</div>
                        <div style="font-size:12px;color:#667799;">橙色预警</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="forecast-item">
                        <div class="forecast-time">今日累计件量</div>
                        <div class="forecast-value" style="color:#4fc3f7;">85,000</div>
                        <div style="font-size:12px;color:#667799;">预计今日 95,000</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="forecast-item">
                        <div class="forecast-time">SLA达标率</div>
                        <div class="forecast-value" style="color:#4caf50;">98.2%</div>
                        <div style="font-size:12px;color:#667799;">目标≥98%</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 各环节预警 -->
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-title">
                    <span>🚨 实时环节预警</span>
                    <span class="badge">红色：2 | 橙色：1 | 黄色：0</span>
                </div>
                <div class="alert-gauge scrollable" style="flex:1;">
                    <div class="gauge-item red">
                        <span class="gauge-label">🔴 分拣线</span>
                        <span class="gauge-value red">95%</span>
                        <div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress-fill" style="width:95%;background:#f44336;"></div></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="gauge-item red">
                        <span class="gauge-label">🔴 缓冲区</span>
                        <span class="gauge-value red">92%</span>
                        <div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress-fill" style="width:92%;background:#f44336;"></div></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="gauge-item orange">
                        <span class="gauge-label">🟠 卸车口</span>
                        <span class="gauge-value orange">88%</span>
                        <div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress-fill" style="width:88%;background:#ff9800;"></div></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="gauge-item green">
                        <span class="gauge-label">🟢 打板区</span>
                        <span class="gauge-value green">72%</span>
                        <div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress-fill" style="width:72%;background:#4caf50;"></div></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="gauge-item green">
                        <span class="gauge-label">🟢 装车区</span>
                        <span class="gauge-value green">65%</span>
                        <div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress-fill" style="width:65%;background:#4caf50;"></div></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="gauge-item orange">
                        <span class="gauge-label">🟠 叉车利用率</span>
                        <span class="gauge-value orange">89%</span>
                        <div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress-fill" style="width:89%;background:#ff9800;"></div></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 实时建议与预测 -->
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-title">
                    <span>💡 实时建议</span>
                    <span class="badge">基于AI分析</span>
                </div>
                <div class="scrollable" style="flex:1;">
                    <ul class="suggestion-list">
                        <li class="suggestion-item">
                            <span class="icon priority-high">🔴</span>
                            <span>分拣线需增5人（当前人效不足，缺口达30%）</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="suggestion-item">
                            <span class="icon priority-high">🔴</span>
                            <span>缓冲区即将爆仓，立即启动装车加速</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="suggestion-item">
                            <span class="icon priority-medium">🟠</span>
                            <span>未来1小时有3辆干线到港，准备3个卸车口</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="suggestion-item">
                            <span class="icon priority-low">🟢</span>
                            <span>打板区能力充足，可适当调整人员支援分拣</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 底部预测 -->
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-title">
                    <span>📈 未来2小时预测（基于预到货量）</span>
                    <span class="badge">干线预报 + 历史模型</span>
                </div>
                <div class="forecast-grid">
                    <div class="forecast-item" style="background:rgba(244,67,54,0.1);border:1px solid #f44336;">
                        <div class="forecast-time">14:00 - 15:00</div>
                        <div class="forecast-value" style="color:#f44336;">12,000</div>
                        <div style="font-size:12px;color:#f44336;">利用率120% 🔴</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="forecast-item" style="background:rgba(255,152,0,0.1);border:1px solid #ff9800;">
                        <div class="forecast-time">15:00 - 16:00</div>
                        <div class="forecast-value" style="color:#ff9800;">10,500</div>
                        <div style="font-size:12px;color:#ff9800;">利用率105% 🟠</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="forecast-item" style="background:rgba(76,175,80,0.1);border:1px solid #4caf50;">
                        <div class="forecast-time">16:00 - 17:00</div>
                        <div class="forecast-value" style="color:#4caf50;">8,000</div>
                        <div style="font-size:12px;color:#4caf50;">利用率80% 🟢</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 人员调配 -->
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-title">
                    <span>👷 人员调配建议</span>
                    <span class="badge">缺口：+8人</span>
                </div>
                <div class="scrollable" style="flex:1;">
                    <ul class="suggestion-list">
                        <li class="suggestion-item">
                            <span class="icon priority-low">🟢</span>
                            <span>从辅助岗调拨：2人</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="suggestion-item">
                            <span class="icon priority-medium">🟠</span>
                            <span>启用备班人员：3人</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="suggestion-item">
                            <span class="icon priority-high">🔴</span>
                            <span>联系外包公司：3人</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 班次看板视图（隐藏） -->
        <div id="view-shift" class="main-content layout-shift view-hidden">
            <div class="card shift-summary">
                <div class="card-title">
                    <span>📊 班次看板：白班 08:00-18:00</span>
                    <span class="badge">剩余：1.5小时</span>
                </div>
                <div class="forecast-grid">
                    <div class="forecast-item">
                        <div class="forecast-time">累计件量</div>
                        <div class="forecast-value" style="color:#4fc3f7;">85,000</div>
                        <div style="font-size:12px;color:#667799;">预计 90,000</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="forecast-item">
                        <div class="forecast-time">峰值利用率</div>
                        <div class="forecast-value" style="color:#f44336;">112%</div>
                        <div style="font-size:12px;color:#667799;">红色预警</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="forecast-item">
                        <div class="forecast-time">平均人效</div>
                        <div class="forecast-value" style="color:#4caf50;">102%</div>
                        <div style="font-size:12px;color:#667799;">标准人效以上</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-title">
                    <span>🔍 瓶颈环节分析（本班次）</span>
                    <span class="badge">根因分析</span>
                </div>
                <div class="scrollable" style="flex:1;">
                    <div style="margin-bottom:12px;">
                        <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:13px;margin-bottom:4px;">
                            <span>1. 分拣线 (时间占比: 60%)</span>
                            <span style="color:#ff9800;">到货集中 + 缺人4个</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="progress-bar" style="width:100%;"><div class="progress-fill" style="width:60%;background:#ff9800;"></div></div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="margin-bottom:12px;">
                        <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:13px;margin-bottom:4px;">
                            <span>2. 卸车口 (时间占比: 25%)</span>
                            <span style="color:#4fc3f7;">预到件延误</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="progress-bar" style="width:100%;"><div class="progress-fill" style="width:25%;background:#4fc3f7;"></div></div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:13px;margin-bottom:4px;">
                            <span>3. 打板区 (时间占比: 15%)</span>
                            <span style="color:#4fc3f7;">装车发车延迟</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="progress-bar" style="width:100%;"><div class="progress-fill" style="width:15%;background:#4fc3f7;"></div></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-title">
                    <span>📋 SOP响应进度</span>
                    <span class="badge">完成率 75%</span>
                </div>
                <div class="scrollable" style="flex:1;">
                    <ul class="suggestion-list">
                        <li class="suggestion-item">
                            <span class="icon" style="color:#4caf50;">✅</span>
                            <span>启动人员调配：从夜班调2人到白班</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="suggestion-item">
                            <span class="icon" style="color:#4caf50;">✅</span>
                            <span>启用备用卸车口：已完成</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="suggestion-item">
                            <span class="icon" style="color:#ff9800;">⏳</span>
                            <span>启动外包：待供应商确认</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="suggestion-item">
                            <span class="icon" style="color:#f44336;">❌</span>
                            <span>紧急采购耗材：未响应</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-title">
                    <span>⚠️ 本班次预警统计</span>
                    <span class="badge">预警触发：4次</span>
                </div>
                <div style="flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;justify-content:center;">
                    <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;justify-content:center;">
                        <div style="text-align:center;">
                            <div style="font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:#f44336;">1</div>
                            <div style="font-size:12px;color:#667799;">红色</div>
                        </div>
                        <div style="text-align:center;">
                            <div style="font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:#ff9800;">2</div>
                            <div style="font-size:12px;color:#667799;">橙色</div>
                        </div>
                        <div style="text-align:center;">
                            <div style="font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:#ffeb3b;">1</div>
                            <div style="font-size:12px;color:#667799;">黄色</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="text-align:center;font-size:13px;color:#667799;">
                        影响件量：12,500件
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 日级分析 / 精益管理版（隐藏） -->
        <div id="view-daily" class="main-content layout-daily view-hidden">
            <div class="card daily-summary">
                <div class="card-title">
                    <span>📈 精益管理版 · 2024-01-15</span>
                    <span class="badge">每日终了更新</span>
                </div>
                <div class="forecast-grid">
                    <div class="forecast-item">
                        <div class="forecast-time">本周平均利用率</div>
                        <div class="forecast-value" style="color:#4fc3f7;">85%</div>
                        <div style="font-size:12px;color:#667799;">安全能力 75%</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="forecast-item">
                        <div class="forecast-time">本周峰值利用率</div>
                        <div class="forecast-value" style="color:#f44336;">120%</div>
                        <div style="font-size:12px;color:#667799;">超极限能力</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="forecast-item">
                        <div class="forecast-time">超安全天数</div>
                        <div class="forecast-value" style="color:#ff9800;">3天</div>
                        <div style="font-size:12px;color:#667799;">本周已发生</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card bottleneck-chart">
                <div class="card-title">
                    <span>🔬 瓶颈环节排名（周累计）</span>
                    <span class="badge">红色预警时长</span>
                </div>
                <div class="scrollable" style="flex:1;">
                    <div style="margin-bottom:10px;">
                        <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:13px;margin-bottom:4px;">
                            <span>1. 分拣线</span>
                            <span style="color:#f44336;font-weight:700;">28小时</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="progress-bar" style="width:100%;height:10px;"><div class="progress-fill" style="width:70%;background:#f44336;"></div></div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="margin-bottom:10px;">
                        <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:13px;margin-bottom:4px;">
                            <span>2. 卸车口</span>
                            <span style="color:#ff9800;font-weight:700;">12小时</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="progress-bar" style="width:100%;height:10px;"><div class="progress-fill" style="width:30%;background:#ff9800;"></div></div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:13px;margin-bottom:4px;">
                            <span>3. 打板区</span>
                            <span style="color:#4fc3f7;font-weight:700;">8小时</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="progress-bar" style="width:100%;height:10px;"><div class="progress-fill" style="width:20%;background:#4fc3f7;"></div></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-title">
                    <span>👥 人机料法环</span>
                    <span class="badge">月度分析</span>
                </div>
                <div class="scrollable" style="flex:1;">
                    <div class="gauge-item green">
                        <span class="gauge-label">👤 分拣员离职率</span>
                        <span class="gauge-value green">15%</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="gauge-item orange">
                        <span class="gauge-label">👤 平均加班时长</span>
                        <span class="gauge-value orange">2.3h/班</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="gauge-item green">
                        <span class="gauge-label">⚙️ 叉车故障率</span>
                        <span class="gauge-value green">3%</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="gauge-item green">
                        <span class="gauge-label">⚙️ 传送带停机</span>
                        <span class="gauge-value green">1次/月</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="gauge-item green">
                        <span class="gauge-label">📋 SOP执行率</span>
                        <span class="gauge-value green">92%</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="gauge-item green">
                        <span class="gauge-label">🌡️ 安全事件</span>
                        <span class="gauge-value green">0</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-title">
                    <span>📐 能力模型</span>
                    <span class="badge">本周趋势</span>
                </div>
                <div id="capacityChart" class="chart-container" style="min-height:140px;"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="card optimization-panel">
                <div class="card-title">
                    <span>💡 本周优化建议</span>
                    <span class="badge">持续改进</span>
                </div>
                <div class="scrollable" style="flex:1;max-height:120px;">
                    <ul class="suggestion-list">
                        <li class="suggestion-item">
                            <span class="icon priority-high">🔴</span>
                            <span>增加分拣线编制2人 → 减少红色预警时长预计30%</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="suggestion-item">
                            <span class="icon priority-medium">🟠</span>
                            <span>优化卸车口排班模式 → 减少等待时间15%</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="suggestion-item">
                            <span class="icon priority-low">🟢</span>
                            <span>启动叉车预防性维护 → 降低故障率至1%以下</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 配置面板 -->
        <div id="configPanel" class="config-panel">
            <div class="config-content">
                <button class="config-close" onclick="closeConfig()">×</button>
                <h2 style="color:#4fc3f7;margin-bottom:16px;">⚙️ 参数配置（可编辑）</h2>
                <table class="config-table">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>参数类别</th>
                            <th>参数名称</th>
                            <th>默认值</th>
                            <th>单位</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr><td>能力基准</td><td>卸车口设计能力</td><td><input type="text" value="1000"></td><td>件/小时</td></tr>
                        <tr><td>能力基准</td><td>分拣线设计能力</td><td><input type="text" value="500"></td><td>件/小时/线</td></tr>
                        <tr><td>能力基准</td><td>打板区设计能力</td><td><input type="text" value="300"></td><td>件/小时/板</td></tr>
                        <tr><td>预警阈值</td><td>绿色线 (%)</td><td><input type="text" value="80"></td><td>% 利用率</td></tr>
                        <tr